'''Maikel Das''' is a German writer, artist, editor, and publisher and a regular contributer for the [[Official German Star Wars Fan Club]] magazine. He also contributed reports and illustrations to the US fanzine Blue Harvest (Zine) from 1994 to 2000.

The illustrations of [[Ishin-Il-Raz]] appearing in [[Star Wars Insider 66|''Star Wars Insider'' 66]] and ''[[Star Wars Insider 84|84]]'' were based on Das.

